---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

---
<Base
  title="White-label CGM patient app for healthcare brands"
  description="Discover the EverCheck CGM app with real-time glucose readings, trend visualization, predictive alerts, historical analytics, and healthcare platform integration support."
>
<style>
* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }
body {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  color:var(--brand-black);
  background:var(--white);
  line-height:1.6;
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
}
/* ===== NAV ===== */

/* ===== NAV DROPDOWN ===== */
/* ===== HERO ===== */
.hero {
  padding:140px 0 100px;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg, #f0f6fb 0%, var(--white) 100%);
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.hero::before {
  content:''; position:absolute; top:-200px; right:-100px;
  width:600px; height:600px; border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(128,188,226,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
  z-index:1;
}
.hero-inner {
  position:relative; z-index:2;
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto;
  align-items:center; gap:80px;
  max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto;
}
.hero-text {
  max-width:560px;
}
.hero-text h1 {
  font-size:52px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.15;
  letter-spacing:-1.5px; margin-bottom:24px; color:var(--brand-black);
}
.hero-text h1 .highlight { color:var(--brand-blue); }
.hero-text p {
  font-size:18px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--brand-gray);
  margin-bottom:36px;
}
.hero-cta { display:flex; gap:16px; }
.hero-phone {
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center;
}
.hero-phone img {
  height:500px; width:auto; border-radius:24px;
  box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}
.hero-clarity-note {
  font-size:11px; color:var(--brand-gray); text-align:center;
  margin-top:12px; opacity:0.7; font-style:italic;
}

/* ===== SECTIONS COMMON ===== */

/* ===== APP OVERVIEW (annotated layout) ===== */
.overview-layout {
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr; gap:40px;
  align-items:center; max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto;
}
.overview-phone { text-align:center; }
.overview-phone img {
  height:580px; width:auto; border-radius:24px;
  box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
}
.overview-annotations { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:28px; }
.overview-annotations.right { text-align:right; }
.overview-annotation h4 {
  font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:var(--brand-black);
  margin-bottom:6px;
}
.overview-annotation p {
  font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; color:var(--brand-gray);
}
.overview-annotation .dot {
  display:inline-block; width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--brand-blue); margin-right:8px;
}
.overview-annotations.right .overview-annotation .dot { margin-right:0; margin-left:8px; }

/* ===== COMMERCIALIZATION CARDS ===== */
.comm-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:28px; }
.comm-grid.col2 { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); }
.comm-card {
  background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg);
  padding:36px 32px; border:1px solid var(--brand-border);
  transition:all 0.3s ease;
}
.comm-card:hover {
  transform:translateY(-4px); box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);
  border-color:transparent;
}
.comm-card .icon-wrap {
  width:48px; height:48px; border-radius:50%;
  background:rgba(128,188,226,0.10); display:flex;
  align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:20px;
}
.comm-card .icon-wrap svg {
  width:24px; height:24px; stroke:var(--brand-blue);
  fill:none; stroke-width:1.8; stroke-linecap:round; stroke-linejoin:round;
}
.comm-card h4 {
  font-size:17px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:10px; color:var(--brand-black);
}
.comm-card p {
  font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--brand-gray);
}

/* ===== FEATURE ROWS (colored blocks, left-right alternating) ===== */
.app-features-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0; }
.app-feature-row { background:#edf4fa; }
.app-feature-row:nth-child(even) { background:var(--brand-black); }
.app-feature-row .app-feature-inner {
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:64px; align-items:center;
  max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 24px;
}
.app-feature-row.reverse .app-feature-inner { direction:rtl; }
.app-feature-row.reverse .app-feature-inner > * { direction:ltr; }
.app-feature-img {
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  padding:20px;
}
.app-feature-img img {
  max-width:300px; max-height:560px; width:auto; height:auto;
  object-fit:contain; border-radius:var(--radius-lg);
}
.app-feature-text {
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center;
}
.app-feature-text h3 {
  font-size:28px; font-weight:650; line-height:1.25;
  letter-spacing:-0.6px; margin-bottom:20px; color:var(--brand-black);
}
.app-feature-text p {
  font-size:15px; line-height:1.75; color:var(--brand-gray); margin-bottom:16px;
}
.app-feature-row:nth-child(even) .app-feature-text h3 { color:var(--white); }
.app-feature-row:nth-child(even) .app-feature-text p { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }

/* ===== SCENARIO CARDS ===== */
.scenario-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:28px; }
.scenario-card {
  background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg);
  padding:40px 32px; text-align:center; border:1px solid var(--brand-border);
  transition:all 0.3s ease;
}
.scenario-card:hover {
  transform:translateY(-4px); box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);
  border-color:transparent;
}
.scenario-card .scenario-icon {
  width:64px; height:64px; border-radius:50%;
  background:rgba(128,188,226,0.12); display:flex;
  align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin:0 auto 24px;
}
.scenario-card .scenario-icon svg {
  width:28px; height:28px; stroke:var(--brand-blue);
  fill:none; stroke-width:1.8; stroke-linecap:round; stroke-linejoin:round;
}
.scenario-card h4 {
  font-size:18px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:12px; color:var(--brand-black);
}
.scenario-card p {
  font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--brand-gray);
}

/* ===== TURNKEY vs INTEGRATION ===== */
.dual-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:32px; }
.dual-card {
  background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg);
  padding:48px 40px; border:1px solid var(--brand-border);
  transition:all 0.3s ease; position:relative;
}
.dual-card.featured {
  border-color:var(--brand-blue);
  box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(128,188,226,0.15);
}
.dual-card h3 {
  font-size:26px; font-weight:650; margin-bottom:20px;
  letter-spacing:-0.5px;
}
.dual-card .dual-list {
  list-style:none; margin-bottom:28px;
}
.dual-card .dual-list li {
  font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--brand-gray);
  padding:8px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--brand-border);
  display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;
}
.dual-card .dual-list li:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.dual-card .dual-list li::before {
  content:'';
  display:inline-block; width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--brand-blue); margin-top:9px; flex-shrink:0;
}
.dual-card .dual-label {
  font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--brand-gray);
  text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px;
  margin-bottom:4px;
}
.dual-card .dual-value {
  font-size:15px; color:var(--brand-black); font-weight:500;
}

/* ===== FAQ ===== */
/* ===== FOOTER CTA ===== */

/* ===== FOOTER ===== */

/* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
</style>

<!-- NAV -->


<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>EverCheck <span class="highlight">CGM app</span> for mobile</h1>
        <p>A patient-ready continuous glucose monitoring app built for your brand. Access real-time glucose readings, predictive alerts, and trend visualization, fully customizable for various healthcare commercialization needs.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-phone">
        <img src="/cgm-app-overview-final.jpg" alt="Annotated overview of the EverCheck CGM patient app on a smartphone. Labels highlight: real-time glucose value (updated every 5 minutes) showing 7.8 mmol/L with trend arrow; sensor component connection status; glucose change indicator arrow; remaining sensor duration and details; optional display of 3h/6h/12h/24h data graphs (3h by default); custom upper and lower reminder limits; glucose target range; event log; historical records; and glucose data analysis and statistics.">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- BUILT FOR COMMERCIALIZATION -->
<section class="section" id="commercialization">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Built for healthcare commercialization</h2>
      <p>More than a glucose monitoring app. A white-label platform designed for healthcare brands to go to market with their own identity.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="comm-grid col2">
      <div class="comm-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Brand customization</h4>
        <p>Customize app logos, colors, language settings, user interfaces, and localized workflows to better align with your regional healthcare market and commercialization strategy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comm-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>API &amp; SDK integration</h4>
        <p>Connect the app to your existing patient management platform, EMR, or telehealth system through documented APIs and SDKs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comm-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Regulatory support</h4>
        <p>Guidance through medical device app approval processes in your target market, with documentation packages built for regulatory submission.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="comm-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Continuous updates</h4>
        <p>We maintain the core app infrastructure &mdash; bug fixes, OS compatibility updates, and feature upgrades &mdash; so your brand always runs the latest version.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding:32px 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <h2>EverCheck patient app features</h2>
      <p>A complete set of patient-focused glucose management features, ready for your brand.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURE 1: Real-time glucose monitoring -->
<div class="app-features-list" id="features">
  <div class="app-feature-row">
    <div class="app-feature-inner">
      <div class="app-feature-text">
        <h3>Real-time glucose monitoring</h3>
        <p>Stay informed with real-time glucose updates, automatically synced from your CGM sensor to your phone and smartwatch.</p>
        <p>Current reading, trend arrow, and 24-hour glucose chart are displayed clearly on one screen, making it easy to track glucose changes at a glance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-feature-img">
        <img src="/cgm-app-phone-2.png" alt="Real-time glucose monitoring screen on EverCheck CGM app">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<!-- FEATURE 2: Glucose trend visualization -->
  <div class="app-feature-row reverse">
    <div class="app-feature-inner">
      <div class="app-feature-text">
        <h3>Glucose trend visualization &amp; prediction</h3>
        <p>View glucose trends over 3, 6, 12, and 24 hours with an intuitive line chart. Directional arrows show where your glucose is heading, helping you make informed decisions about meals, exercise, and insulin.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-feature-img">
        <img src="/cgm-app-phone-3.png" alt="Glucose trend visualization and prediction chart on EverCheck CGM app">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<!-- FEATURE 3: High/low glucose alerts -->
  <div class="app-feature-row">
    <div class="app-feature-inner">
      <div class="app-feature-text">
        <h3>High/low glucose alerts</h3>
        <p>Set personalized high and low glucose thresholds and receive timely alerts when your glucose approaches or exceeds these limits, helping you take proactive action.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-feature-img">
        <img src="/cgm-app-phone-4.png" alt="High and low glucose alert configuration on EverCheck CGM app">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<!-- FEATURE 4: Event logging -->
  <div class="app-feature-row reverse">
    <div class="app-feature-inner">
      <div class="app-feature-text">
        <h3>Event logging</h3>
        <p>Log meals, exercise, insulin doses, and medication with just a few taps. Each event is timestamped and overlaid on your glucose trend chart, helping you connect daily activities with glucose changes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-feature-img">
        <img src="/cgm-app-phone-1.png" alt="Event logging screen for meals, exercise and insulin on EverCheck CGM app">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<!-- FEATURE 5: History records & statistics -->
  <div class="app-feature-row">
    <div class="app-feature-inner">
      <div class="app-feature-text">
        <h3>History records &amp; statistics</h3>
        <p>Review daily, weekly, and monthly glucose summaries with key metrics including time-in-range, average glucose, and estimated HbA1c. Generate detailed reports to share with your healthcare provider.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-feature-img">
        <img src="/cgm-app-phone-2.png" alt="Historical glucose statistics and analytics dashboard on EverCheck CGM app">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TURNKEY vs INTEGRATION -->
<section class="section section-alt" id="deployment">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Choose your deployment model</h2>
      <p>Two flexible paths to bring a CGM app to your market &mdash; pick the one that fits your infrastructure.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="dual-grid">
      <div class="dual-card featured">
        <h3>White-label app</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px; color:var(--brand-gray); margin-bottom:24px;">A ready-to-launch CGM app with your brand identity. We handle the technology; you focus on go-to-market.</p>
        <div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
          <div class="dual-label">Best for</div>
          <div class="dual-value">Brands that want to launch quickly without building a software team</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="dual-list">
          <li>Full app with your brand name, logo, and colors</li>
          <li>Pre-configured CGM sensor pairing and data pipeline</li>
          <li>App store submission support (iOS &amp; Android)</li>
          <li>Ongoing maintenance and OS compatibility updates</li>
          <li>Patient onboarding materials available for co-branding</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="dual-card">
        <h3>API &amp; SDK access</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px; color:var(--brand-gray); margin-bottom:24px;">Connect CGM data into your existing patient platform or build your own app on top of our SDK.</p>
        <div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
          <div class="dual-label">Best for</div>
          <div class="dual-value">Brands with an existing healthcare platform or in-house development team</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="dual-list">
          <li>RESTful API for glucose data ingestion into your system</li>
          <li>SDK documentation for building custom patient-facing features</li>
          <li>Technical integration support from our engineering team</li>
          <li>Sandbox environment for development and testing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question"><span class="faq-text">Can we customize the glucose alert thresholds for our target patient population?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. Alert thresholds for high glucose, low glucose, and predictive warnings are fully configurable. We can pre-set default thresholds based on your target patient demographics &mdash; pediatric, adult, or gestational &mdash; and individual patients can further personalize them within the app.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question"><span class="faq-text">How do app updates work for white-label deployments?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We manage the core app release cycle. When a new version is ready &mdash; with bug fixes, OS compatibility updates, or new features &mdash; we provide the update through your branded app listing on the App Store and Google Play. Your patients receive the update just like any other app update, with your brand identity intact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question"><span class="faq-text">Do you provide patient onboarding materials we can co-brand?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. We provide a full set of onboarding assets &mdash; quick-start guides, tutorial videos, and in-app walkthrough screens &mdash; that can be co-branded with your logo and design language. These materials are available in all supported languages.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER CTA -->
<section class="section" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-cta">
      <h2>Ready to bring your branded CGM app to market?</h2>
      <p>Talk to our team about white-label deployment, API integration, or a custom demo tailored to your market.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact us now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

</Base>
